headline: Palantir Cognizant AI Push Tests High Valuation And Weak Momentum
summary: Palantir Technologies and Cognizant have expanded their partnership to speed up AI driven modernization in healthcare and other enterprises. The collaboration uses Palantir's Artificial Intelligence Platform, AIP, to support secure AI deployments in highly regulated settings. This development highlights Palantir's push beyond government contracts into broader commercial and compliance focused markets.
